query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `partner_activation_codes` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
  `partnerId` int NOT NULL,
  `code` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `codeType` enum('single_use','multi_use') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'single_use',
  `maxUses` int,
  `usesCount` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `status` enum('active','used','expired','revoked') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'active',
  `billingCycle` enum('monthly','yearly') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'monthly',
  `durationMonths` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 12,
  `expiresAt` timestamp,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX `activation_codes_code_unique` (`code`),
  INDEX `activation_codes_partner_idx` (`partnerId`),
  INDEX `activation_codes_status_idx` (`status`)
);
